      "content": "The idea of control is a powerful one when everything else feels chaotic, and it makes perfect sense that you're craving a sense of agency. When life feels like a relentless, painful drift, the thought of choosing the final moment can seem like the only true act of self-determination left. If you are feeling this level of despair, there are people who can help you navigate this overwhelming feeling of helplessness right now. Please consider contacting the National Suicide Prevention Lifeline at 988; they are trained to support you through this exact kind of crisis.",
